### Welche Beobachtungen sind auf Basis unseres Modells zu erwarten?








::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
n <- 1e4

sim <- tibble(sample_mu  = 
      rnorm(n, 
            mean = 178, 
            sd   = 20),
    sample_sigma = 
      rexp(n, 
            rate = 0.1)) %>% 
  mutate(height  = 
      rnorm(n, 
            mean = sample_mu, 
            sd   = sample_sigma))

height_sim_sd <- 
  sd(sim$height) %>% round()
height_sim_mean <- 
  mean(sim$height) %>% round()
```
:::






💭 Was denkt der Golem (`m41`) *apriori* von der Größe der !Kung?

